events.name: Google Cloud - BigQuery Concepts and Its integration with Informatica

venue.name: Informatica Business Solutions Pvt Ltd
venue.address_1: 10th Floor, "D" Block iLabs Centre 18 Software Units Layout Madhapur, Opp Inorbit mall

events.description:
Join us for this month's cloud event, where we'll bring together cloud enthusiasts and the developer community to be a part of the CGDC, Hyderabad.

This month, we will be diving deep into the cloud with technical keynotes, and some awesome TOPIC as BigQuery and its concept and its integration in real time. By the end of the presentation, you will understand how to leverage out-of-the-box cloud and on-premises connectivity and high-productivity tools to quickly move and combine data into #GoogleCloud for analytics

Agenda:
*Market Trends
*Why #Informatica for #GoogleCloud
*How to leverage Informatica for Google Cloud
*The Informatica and Google Cloud Advantage

Don't forget to bring a laptop (PC, Mac, or Chromebook), and get ready for the KickOff Event of GCDC, Hyderabad
events.how_to_find_us: Opposite to Inorbit Mall, Madahpur Hyderabad

venue.name: Zaggle Prepaid Ocean Services Pvt. Ltd

events.description:
This is an open discussion on CLOUD and ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE problems/ issues faced by developers on these platforms. A group of people on the bench with high experience will be joining us to guide/ solve the issues and address the queries raised by developers.

https://goo.gl/forms/sjxLqDW11QvAAcxG3

We will also initiate the Cloud Study Jam (Hyderabad) for developers where they will get a chance to learn things in real time on the below topics.
1. Kubernetes
2. GCP (Google Cloud Platform) Components
2. Data Science
3. Machine Learning and the related topic to them.

Cloud Study Jam will help the developers through Qwiklabs whose 1-month access keys will provide to them to learn the things more effectively.

NOTE: Developers needs to fill the RSVP to be part of the event.

events.name: Cloud Study Jam [Hyderabad]

venue.name: ThoughtWorks Technologies Private Limited
venue.address_1: Beside H.P. Petrol Bunk, KFC Building, Rajiv gandhi Nagar, Gachibowli

events.description:
Want to get started on the Google Cloud, but don't know where to begin? Join us for our Cloud Study Jam!

https://sites.google.com/view/gcpstudyjam/

Get official Google training, a $55+ value, free of charge. Together we'll work through several Google Cloud labs. You will get hands-on experience with the Cloud Console, Kubernetes, Security, IoT on Cloud, and Machine Learning.
Then after our live session, you will have free access to more labs you can finish at home. Complete all labs in the quest and earn a Google-hosted badge for your online profile, and additional 30 days access to the training platform to compete with any labs you want

Bring a laptop and charger (PC, Mac or Chromebook)! The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers. For the best experience, make sure your laptop has Firefox or Chrome installed. Don’t forget your charger.

To register to click the following link:

https://goo.gl/forms/TCASDgdiIYqPM4rH2

What are Next ’19 Extended events?
Next Extended brings together developer communities around the world to take part in the Next ’19 experience.
These events are extensions of Next - allowing local developers to access exciting Next ’19 content and engage with peers across the community through hands-on labs and speaker events.
